ca.mcgill.ecse211.finalproject.controller

Class Controller

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • ca.mcgill.ecse211.finalproject.controller.Controller
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UltrasonicController, java.lang.Runnable

    public class Controller
extends java.lang.Thread
implements UltrasonicController
    Controls sequence of events between block detection, navigation, obstacle avoidance, and zipline traversal. The class Controller is started in main. Controller takes care of localizing the robot, and deciding and controlling the state of the robot to accomplish the tasks at hand to complete the challenge.
